query:
SELECT DISTINCT operadora_1 as convenio FROM pacientes WHERE operadora_1 IS NOT NULL AND operadora_1 != ''
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT operadora_2 FROM pacientes WHERE operadora_2 IS NOT NULL AND operadora_2 != ''
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT convenio FROM atendimentos WHERE convenio IS NOT NULL AND convenio != ''
ORDER BY convenio;
